    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8003-8bda-fd45065d7237",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper proposes a KT model that incorporates data from multiple resource types - Multiview Knowledge Model (MVKM) using tensor factorization - which is meant to be able to reduce dimensionality. The authors perform multiple tests for predictive accuracy and curiously the authors found multiple similarities across different types of learning materials. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8003-8bda-fd45065d7237",
        "parent": {
